{"tid":1696680,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[實事] 入黎回報你公司黃/藍  反唔反對罷工 !!!! 建立全面黃色經濟圈","createTime":"2019-11-06T10:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T03:26:45.000Z","uid":105976,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"fef911d5b2f437ee10b7825ee80a0f3b6111b650","tid":1696680,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T10:00:03.000Z","msg":"罷工就大部份人都想罷 但驚被清算 &amp; 經濟壓力<br />\n<br />\n呢份清單主要目標唔係要d大中型公司明目張膽地顯黃<br />\n大中企業都會驚得失任何一方 <br />\n佢地中立, 唔清算罷工就已經足夠<br />\n<br />\n但如果一入左藍名單 肯定生意會受打擊<br />\n黃爆買 藍罷買<br />\n呢個就係我地目的  將黃色經濟圈由下而上繼續擴散<br />\n<br />\n暫時分做接近20幾個行業<br />\n1. 餐飲&amp;食物, 3. 工程&amp;維修 4. 運輸&amp;物流 7. 批發&amp;貿易 etc<br />\n<br />\n匿名提供公司資料 (可以唔留contact, 最好有prove):<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/Rdf3Kmrv1EipmBuTA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FRdf3Kmrv1EipmBuTA&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnXwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=5a55aa1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/Rdf3Kmrv1EipmBuTA</a><br />\n<br />\n清單總覽: (等有DATA之後會整好睇d)<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1nygIK04RBUXt6c1pTKqChpEFBLDnahpJ-pbJhdvZwEg/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1nygIK04RBUXt6c1pTKqChpEFBLDnahpJ-pbJhdvZwEg%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=5WD1fpiCBK613UyTU9OnXwy7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=ad44cdc3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1nygIK04RBUXt6c1pTKqChpEFBLDnahpJ-pbJhdvZwEg/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n順便推埋呢個post: 三罷陣線：各行各業都要人<br />\n入去join埋自己行業既telegram group<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1696517/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1696517/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n各group admin可唔可以幫手feed in 公司藍黃中立資料"},{"pid":"14f925f3e6812453e562af9edc8a00d874f66d59","tid":1696680,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-06T10:00:42.000Z","msg":"快d feed多d資料入黎<br />\n做實事就冇人推<br />\n<br />\n8掛新聞就圍住